POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; CALIFORNIA -- FINANCES; CHILDREN -- HEALTH; CHILDREN -- 
EDUCATION; POVERTY; FEINSTEIN, DIANNE; WILSON, PETE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
