EMPLOYEE THEFT; MONEY LAUNDERING; TAX EVASION; EXTORTION; POLICE -- LOS ANGELES 
COUNTY; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; SOBEL, ROBERT R 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
