BETTING WITH JANICE; 
</P>
<P>
THE REMATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mysterious Pirate, a chalk starter and a show finisher in the sixth, cost me my 
largest loss of the meet. I will try to rebound today, betting $50 to win and 
place on Franny Frizzle in the seventh. 
</P>
<P>
Janice Goldinger's Thu. Bankroll: $1,949 
</P>
<P>
Thursday's Loss: $150 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $1,799 
</P>
<P>
SURELOCK lost $100 when Past Remembered failed to win the eighth. However, his 
other two exacta horses in the race, Bequest and Girl Of France netted him $60 
to cut his losses to $40 for the day. His selection today is $200 to win on 
Formidable Lady in the eighth. 
</P>
<P>
